      "text": [
        "1739 - وَ سُئِلَ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ: أَيُّ اَلصَّدَقَةِ أَفْضَلُ قَالَ «عَلَى ذِي اَلرَّحِمِ اَلْكَاشِحِ »."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.1739 - Imam (as) was asked: \"Which charity is the best?\"\nImam (as) replied: \"To a relative who harbors enmity (against you).\""
        ]
      }
    }
